flutter_rating_bar.description: A simple yet fully customizable ratingbar for flutter which also include a rating bar indicator, supporting any fraction of rating.

youtube_player_iframe.description: Flutter port of the official YouTube iFrame player API. Supports web & mobile platforms.

flutter_tagging.description: A flutter package with tagging or multiselect functionality. Useful for adding Tag or Label Selection Forms.
